<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Privacy Policy | Stack and Sleep</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Stack and Sleep privacy policy — how we collect, use, and protect your data." />
  <meta name="robots" content="index, follow" />
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://stackandsleep.com/privacy-policy/" />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/global.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/nav.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/cards.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/article.css" />
</head>
<body class="article-page">

  <div class="disclosure-bar">
    Independent reviews — affiliate links at no extra cost to you.&nbsp;
    <a href="/affiliate-disclosure/">Full disclosure</a>&nbsp;·&nbsp;
    <a href="/how-we-review/">How we review</a>
  </div>

  <Nav />

  <main>
    <header class="article-header">
      <div class="article-header-cat">Legal</div>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <div class="article-header-meta">
        <span>Last updated: April 2026</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="article-body">
      <p>This Privacy Policy explains how Stack and Sleep ("we", "us", "our") collects, uses, and protects information when you visit stackandsleep.com. By using this site, you agree to the terms described below.</p>

      <h2>1. Information we collect</h2>
      <p>We collect only the information you voluntarily provide:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Email address</strong> — when you subscribe to our newsletter via the sign-up form on this site</li>
        <li><strong>Name and message</strong> — when you submit our contact form</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We do not collect any other personal data. We do not use tracking pixels, fingerprinting, or behavioural advertising tools.</p>

      <h2>2. How we use your information</h2>
      <p>Your email address is used solely to send our newsletter — sleep optimisation tips, product guides, and updates from Stack and Sleep. We send approximately one email per week.</p>
      <p>Contact form submissions are used only to respond to your enquiry.</p>
      <p>We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>

      <h2>3. Third-party services</h2>
      <p>We use the following third-party services to operate this site:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Airtable</strong> — stores newsletter subscriber email addresses. <a href="https://www.airtable.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Airtable Privacy Policy</a></li>
        <li><strong>Vercel</strong> — hosts this website. Standard server logs (IP address, browser type, pages visited) may be retained briefly for security purposes. <a href="https://vercel.com/legal/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Vercel Privacy Policy</a></li>
        <li><strong>Formspree</strong> — processes contact form submissions. <a href="https://formspree.io/legal/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Formspree Privacy Policy</a></li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. Affiliate links</h2>
      <p>This site contains affiliate links to third-party retailers including Amazon, Impact.com, and ShareASale. When you click an affiliate link, the retailer may set cookies on your browser to track the referral. These cookies are governed by the retailer's own privacy policy. We do not have access to any personal data collected by retailers through these links.</p>

      <h2>5. Cookies</h2>
      <p>This site does not set its own cookies. Third-party affiliate networks may set cookies when you click product links. You can control cookie settings via your browser preferences.</p>

      <h2>6. Data retention</h2>
      <p>We retain your email address for as long as you remain subscribed to our newsletter. Contact form submissions are retained for up to 12 months.</p>

      <h2>7. Your rights</h2>
      <p>You have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Unsubscribe</strong> — click the unsubscribe link in any newsletter email at any time</li>
        <li><strong>Access</strong> — request a copy of the personal data we hold about you</li>
        <li><strong>Deletion</strong> — request that we delete your personal data</li>
        <li><strong>Correction</strong> — request that we correct inaccurate data</li>
      </ul>
      <p>To exercise any of these rights, please use our <a href="/contact/">contact form</a>.</p>

      <h2>8. Children's privacy</h2>
      <p>This site is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal data from children.</p>

      <h2>9. Changes to this policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The "Last updated" date at the top of this page reflects the most recent revision. Continued use of this site after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>

      <h2>10. Contact</h2>
      <p>For any privacy-related questions or requests, please use our <a href="/contact/">contact form</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</body>
</html>
